data.title: Review of Amanda Products Long Travel A-Arm JK Suspension - SEMA 2015
data.tags: SEMA 2015, SEMA, Amanda Products, Long Travel A-Arm JK Suspension
data.description: Originally built as a prototype for manufacturers, this suspension conversion kit takes your ride from solid-axle to independent. Ideal for everything off-road, Amanda’s suspension maintains your stock ride height with up to 16” of usable travel.

asset.title: Amanda Products Long Travel A-Arm JK Suspension - SEMA 2015
asset.description:
Amanda Products’ Long Travel A-Arm Conversion Kit for Jeep Wrangler JK’s could soon be the aftermarket’s next best thing. Originally built as a prototype for manufacturers, this suspension conversion kit takes your ride from solid axle to independent. Ideal for everything off-road, from pre-running in the desert to trail-running, Amanda’s suspension maintains your stock ride height with up to 16” of usable travel. Keep your eyes peeled for Amanda Products hitting aftermarket shelves near you.

Get the inside scoop straight from SEMA 2015.

data.title: SEMA Ignited 2015 - Valyrian Steel Burning Man Vehicle
data.tags: SEMA 2015, SEMA, SEMA Ignited 2015, Valyrian Steel, Burning Man
data.description: Commissioned by artist Henry Chang, the Valyrian Steel vehicle was custom-built for Burning Man.  Handmade from steel tubing and powered by a Ford Coyote 5.0L engine,  this vehicle rolls on 54" Mickey Thompson tires in the rear, supported by Fox Shocks all around.

asset.title: Valyrian Steel Burning Man Vehicle - SEMA Ignited
asset.description:
More SEMA Coverage here: http://www.autoanything.com/sema/2015

Commissioned by artist Henry Chang, the Valyrian Steel vehicle was custom built for Burning Man.  Hand made from steel tubing and powered by a Ford Coyote 5.0L engine,  this vehicle rolls on 54" Mickey Thompson tires in the rear, supported by Fox Shocks all around.
